		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=311252"><span id=Scholar>Samin</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br />50 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.10]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Samin&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>Not tryin to hurt feelings here, but you are crazy if you want to go full archery in EQ, especially&nbsp;&nbsp;pre level 59 with AAs.<br><br>Archery, is, has, and will always be, a secondary form of damage in EQ. It was never intended, from the beginning, to be a viable form of damage dealing. The only thing that changed, was the AAs and good bows you can obtain pre Time, which make it a decent tool at that particular level and point in the game.<br><br>In order to play archer from your level up, you will either need<br>1. Another account to 2 box<br>2. Some mighty good friends that won't mind helping you level<br><br>Otherwise, you will be soloing your way up, because no pickup group is going to allow you to sit back and use archery. It does too little damage, and you will be expected to tank pre 50s anyways, on occation.<br><br>As for things that help archery-<br>Dex. Get as much as you can. <br><br>Until you get post 50, your damage is going to be limited. So concentrate on a low delay bow. You are going to miss alot, and the amount of damage per hit, is going to be minor anyways.<br><br>Get one of those packs from LDoN, that summons hunter's barbs, or at level 45, get a tolans bracer. You are going to need a TON of arrows, and toting around components and making them in this amount, is going to be difficult. Until then, hang around zones that are quick to merchants that carry your components you need to make more arrows. <br><br>Good luck and God bless.</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpa