re doing.<br>Don't know if this was really helping with tips...can't add much to what has been said already..max that dexterity...have way of making arrows when you need them....and continue to upgrade the bow when you can.<br><br>Tanglewood Jones 63 Ranger<br>The Tribunal</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Oktober Festivus<br> Short Mage of the Tribunal</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >0 Replies</td></tr></table>
